The paper presents a deep neural network training approach that utilizes unlabeled data to achieve remarkable classification results. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on training deep neural networks, the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) is the most likely.
